Baseball team wins versus 7 independent variables for National league teams

Data for Exercise 9.23

Format

A data frame with 12 observations on the following 9 variables.

team
a factor with levels Atlanta Chicago Cincinnati Houston Los Angeles Montreal New York Philadelphia Pittsburgh San Diego San Francisco St. Louis
wins
a numeric vector
batavg
a numeric vector
rbi
a numeric vector
stole
a numeric vector
strkout
a numeric vector
caught
a numeric vector
errors
a numeric vector
era
a numeric vector

Examples


str(Wins)
attach(Wins)
plot(era,wins)
model <- lm(wins~era)
abline(model)
summary(model)
detach(Wins)
remove(model)
